name: Ziba

reviews.review_text:
Visited here last week. Really good place, just on the way to Baga beach! The vibe of the place is amazing. They have live music on weekends which elevates the vibe. They have an indoor as well as an outdoor seating.

The cocktails & food are excellent and totally worth the price. A must visit, especially over weekends!

It's a really well set up restaurant located just next to the busy lanes of North Goa and has a beautiful ambience. They offer spacious ambience overlooking beautiful fields, delicious oriental food, cocktails, live music and much more

We tried their special bloody Mary prawns for starters and we totally loved the unique flavours it had. Next we had their Vietnamese chilli fish and I loved every bite of it. The chonak fish was fresh and flavourful.
We also tried their Indonesian fried rice which was sweet, tangy. The chicken steak had tender chicken pieces tossed in flavourful sauce.
For drinks we had fresh orange juice, pineapple juice and lemon soda. It was really chilled and refreshing
For deserts, I had chocolate ice cream. Beautifully served and tasted heavenly.

They also have a live bar serving unique cocktails and mocktails and their ambience spanning over 3 floors is perfect for parties!!

The food was presented beautifully and the quantity was really good. The staff were welcoming and friendly. A must try place for weekend getaways in north goa!!

It was a lovely experience!!!
the food is very tasty and staff are very friendly.
They also do candlelight dinners on advance bookings.

Its a great place if you want to host birthday parties as they curate the menu as per your liking and very flexible.
Me and my friends had a great time..!!

description:
**Ziba: A Culinary Jewel in Arpora**

Nestled conveniently just off the popular route to Baga beach, Ziba has made quite an impression with its impressive rating of 4.5 from a substantial pool of 646 reviews. This restaurant has quickly become a favored destination for locals and tourists alike, offering a delightful blend of cuisine, ambiance, and enticing cocktails—recurring themes that resonate in the glowing feedback from its patrons. Guests frequently rave about the restaurant's vibrant cocktails (16 mentions) and quality food that aligns with its perceived value for money (15 mentions). 

**Ambiance & Design**

Upon arrival, Ziba welcomes with an enchanting atmosphere that beautifully reflects both indoor and outdoor seating options. The photographs convey a spacious dining area adorned with tasteful décor, overlooking picturesque fields that create a tranquil backdrop. You can almost feel the weekend vibe springing to life with live music filling the air, enhancing the dining experience. The illumination is soft yet inviting, perfectly suited for both casual and celebratory occasions. Reviews note the ambiance as "amazing," making it an ideal spot for both energetic groups and serene candlelight dinners—particularly with advanced bookings.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

Ziba's culinary offerings are nothing short of exceptional. Highlighting a diverse menu, guests have particularly praised dishes like the **Bloody Mary Prawns**, showcasing flavors that devour the senses, and the **Vietnamese Chilli Fish**, which reportedly exhibits a delicious balance of moisture and flavor. The **Chonak Fish**, recognized for its freshness, complemented by a delightful **Indonesian Fried Rice**, embodies the restaurant's dedication to quality. 

Each dish is not only lauded for taste but also for its stunning presentation. Patrons share that the quantity exceeds expectations, ensuring that diners leave satisfied. The bar shines with its array of cocktails and mocktails, which guests describe as both refreshing and unique, making for a perfect companion to the savory dishes. Desserts are given equal attention, with the **chocolate ice cream** garnering special acclaim for its delightful sweetness.

**Customer Experience & Service**

The service at Ziba has earned itself accolades for its warmth and efficiency. Customers have consistently noted the friendly demeanor of the staff, who are evidently trained to enhance the dining experience, whether recommending cocktails or curating special birthday menus. Reviews suggest ease when booking reservations, particularly for more intimate candlelight dinners or larger gatherings.

**Popularity & Reviews**

Ziba's reputation continues to grow, hampered not at all by the seeming chaos of North Goa. The vibrant atmosphere, combined with live music, cocktails, and beautifully curated plates, makes for an output of positive feedback across social media platforms and review websites. This restaurant evidently embodies a welcoming spirit, ideal for weekend getaways or casual weekday dinners. It stands out as a must-visit dining destination that locals and travelers alike should include on their itineraries.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

The assortment of customer-provided images not only complements the textual experience but also captures the essence of Ziba's ambiance and culinary artistry. From the inviting outdoor settings to the vibrancy of the cocktails and beautifully arranged plates, each picture captures the very spirit that patrons describe. 

In conclusion, Ziba is more than just a dining location; it's a lively culinary experience waiting to be explored. With its impressive menu, considerate service, and charming ambiance, it’s a restaurant that promises a memorable visit—whether for an energetic meal or a more serene evening under the stars.
